sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Admin as Admin do cliente
    participant API as Lightcode Registration API
    participant Email as E-mail de onboarding
    participant OAuth as OAuth Clients
    participant Schema as Account JSON Schemas
    participant Accounts as Accounts
    participant User as Usuario final

    Admin->>API: POST /api/tenants
    API-->>Email: Enviar Tenant ID, Client ID e Client Secret
    Admin->>OAuth: POST /api/oauth-clients/me definir role admin
    Admin->>API: POST /api/auth/token grant_type=client_credentials
    API-->>Admin: Access token tecnico do cliente
    Admin->>Schema: POST /api/account-json-schemas
    Schema-->>Admin: Schema de cadastro criado
    Admin->>Accounts: POST /api/accounts/admin ou fluxo publico
    Accounts-->>User: Enviar confirmacao de e-mail por codigo ou link
    User->>Accounts: POST /api/accounts/confirm-email-code/{code} ou clicar no link
    Accounts-->>User: E-mail confirmado

    Note over Admin,API: client_credentials autentica a aplicacao cliente e nao aplica 2FA.
    Note over User,Accounts: Confirmacao de e-mail de cadastro nao e 2FA de login.
